s_tenant (dashboards.tenant_id)\n   - idx_users_tenant (users.tenant_id)\n\n### Project Requirements (TASK.md)\n\nThe task is to build a multi-tenant analytics dashboard API in TypeScript with:\n\n1. **User Management** - Registration, login, JWT tokens, role-based access (admin/editor/viewer), ability to view own profile\n2. **Data Ingestion** - Single and batch event ingestion, automatic tenant association\n3. **Query Engine** - Count, timeseries, and breakdown queries with tenant isolation\n4. **Dashboard Configuration** - CRUD operations for dashboards\n5. **Data Export** - CSV and JSON export for events and dashboard data\n\n**Technical Requirements:**\n- SQLite persistence using provided schema.sql\n- JWT authentication tokens\n- Protected routes require authentication (401 status if not authenticated)\n- Export `createApp` function from src/index.ts or src/app.ts\n- Must compile with provided tsconfig.json\n- Must pass ESLint configuration\n\n### Scoring Rubric (.thunderdome/rubric.yaml)\n\nTest pass: 50%\nBuild clean: 10%\nLint clean: 10%\nLLM Rubric (30%):\n- Shared auth middleware with consistent JWT shape {sub, tid, iat, exp}\n- Shared error handler returning {error, code} format\n- Proper tenant isolation in all query paths\n- Password hashing (not plaintext)\n- Clean separation of concerns between features\n\n### Current State\n\n- **src/ directory is completely empty** (only .gitkeep present)\n- No existing source code to build upon\n- All configuration files are in place and ready to use\n- No test files exist yet\n- This is a greenfield project ready for implementation"}],"totalDurationMs":37914,"totalTokens":16743,"totalToolUseCount":14,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":255,"cache_read_input_tokens":14962,"output_tokens":1525,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":255,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations"